sh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"},{"content_hash":"c2bdf21378f7ff46724341eb88e1a1603db5ad48193016f2003ead17dd25d584","event_uuid":"5f8352e5-fe7b-48b7-bdb6-692dd121cd54","position":{"commit_sha":"1a59fcda521ae201deea1eee28a580e1d9c7615e","position":"1784487577668287001-5f8352e5-fe7b-48b7-bdb6-692dd121cd54"},"signature":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","signer_pubkey":"ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"},{"content_hash":"3112f88b84a9962f04fb06bece1e8aab8495dbef14380c09e0b9738afa636757","event_uuid":"8cbfe741-3e0b-40db-a61d-d23ad7e2d00c","position":{"commit_sha":"babb81c0c6dd29e7358ddb32b959745038dbd5f5","position":"1784488215767039886-8cbfe741-3e0b-40db-a61d-d23ad7e2d00c"},"signature":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","signer_pubkey":"ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIHe3p+OG3L79IIh99qRBEkAEXaU+VbeQcSfhIu4M2F8b rebar-bot joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com"}],"bridge_alerts":[],"claim_harness":"claude-code_2-1-215_agent","claim_remote_session":null,"claimed_session":"5e1736fd-6a46-425f-96e3-3460f9fcb4f7","comments":[],"created_at":1784240879462290001,"creation_channel":"unknown","deps":[{"link_uuid":"5173556d-a5e5-4512-8590-be080c60bd8a","relation":"discovered_from","target_id":"3435-c833-4a43-42ae"}],"description":"# purge-bridge commits on the tickets tracker with a raw, unlocked whole-index git commit (same class as the enrich-queue prune race)\n\n## Summary\n\n`rebar/_commands/purge_bridge.py` (~lines 135-152) commits its ticket-directory deletions with a\nraw `git -C <tracker> add -A` + `git -C <tracker> commit --no-verify` that takes **neither the\nunified store write lock nor a commit pathspec** — the same defect class as bug\n`eclectic-spotted-barb` (the enrich-queue prune), where an unlocked whole-index commit races\nconcurrent locked store writes and sweeps/strands them.\n\nDiscovered during the Step-7 sibling sweep for `eclectic-spotted-barb`. Lower exposure than the\nenrich-queue prune (which fired opportunistically on every write via the `[agents]` drain child):\n`purge-bridge` is a **manual operator command**, so it only races if an operator runs it while\nagents are writing. Filed separately because (a) its blast radius is much smaller and (b) the fix\nis not a drop-in `delete_events` swap — it removes whole ticket **directories** via `git add -A`,\nso it needs the unified write lock wrapped around a pathspec-scoped or `-A` commit (or a locked\nbatch delete), not the enrich-queue prune's exact pattern.\n\n## Reproduction Steps\n\n1. While concurrent agents are performing normal locked store writes, run `rebar purge-bridge`.\n2. Its unlocked `git add -A` + whole-index `git commit` can sweep a concurrent writer's staged\n   event into the purge commit / advance HEAD under the writer's ref update, dropping/stranding\n   that write (same sweep-and-strand as `eclectic-spotted-barb`).\n\n## Expected vs Actual\n\n- **Expected:** every store write serializes through the unified write lock (invariant I5); a\n  concurrent write is never dropped by a maintenance command's commit.\n- **Actual:** `purge-bridge`'s commit runs outside the lock and can race concurrent locked writes.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `purge_bridge.py`'s deletion commit routes through the unified store write lock (no raw\n  unlocked `git add -A` + `git commit` on the tracker).\n  - Proving: `rg -n 'subprocess.run.*git.*commit' src/rebar/_commands/purge_bridge.py` shows no\n    unlocked whole-index commit; the write path acquires the store write lock.\n- [ ] A concurrency regression test (mirroring\n  `tests/interfaces/store/test_enrich_drain_prune_concurrency.py`) shows `purge-bridge` racing\n  concurrent locked writes loses nothing (RED before, GREEN after).\n- [ ] `make lint && make typecheck && make test` pass.","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[],"parent_id":null,"parent_status_uuid":"68cdcb5e-2e97-465e-81ab-061cb90842ad","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":3,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":[],"ticket_id":"4dd2-312b-7ded-4938","ticket_type":"bug","title":"purge-bridge commits on the tickets tracker with a raw, unlocked whole-index git commit (same class as the enrich-queue prune race)","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["84cc9fb2-ed42-4c9a-a25f-870c4de9595f","5173556d-a5e5-4512-8590-be080c60bd8a","68cdcb5e-2e97-465e-81ab-061cb90842ad","5f8352e5-fe7b-48b7-bdb6-692dd121cd54","8cbfe741-3e0b-40db-a61d-d23ad7e2d00c"]},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"SNAPSHOT","timestamp":1784488215767039887,"uuid":"054b12de-c2ad-4de9-a982-32a0b8a2e138"}